name: Lightning Earrings
description: New design hell yeah! Old school Swank fans will remember I started out making these beauties from hand cut foam board, but now you can get them in hard wearing, nice and shiney perspex!

name: Octodiver Necklace
description: Brand new design from Swank. I really love octopi, but there are plenty of people making octopi necklaces so I wanted something different,, one day I spotted an old divers helmet in a pub and loved it. So I've stuck it on the octopus and hey presto, the octodiver! The octodiver is laser cut by a small company in the UK and put together by my fair hands. It is cut from blue mirrored perspex and measures 10.5cm across, so it ain't small.

name: Winged Skull Necklace
description: New design whoop whoop! What can I say, it's a skull with wings, it's like Pegasus but without the horse. Choose from gold, silver or amazing new purple mirrored perspex.

name: Lucha Libre Necklace
description: Unleash your inner fighter with this Mexican wrestler mask necklace! Wear this down your local Mexican restaurant to get noticed by the waiter and get some free nachos, or a date if you're that way inclined! The Mexican wrestler mask necklace is laser cut from Perspex and measures a mighty 5.5cm across and 6am high. There are three different colour ways to choose from as well as two different lengths of chain 16" and 24", you can see on the pictures how long these look. I like necklaces short, but am realising slowly that owning a jewellery design company doesn't mean catering to just myself!

name: POW! Necklace
description: Bring out your inner Batman with this retro comic book style POW! necklace. It's laser cut from perspex, comes in bight blue or blue glitter and measures 9cm across.

name: Toucan Necklace
description:
I've noticed that there are a lot of designers out there making bird related jewellery. I have also noticed lots of them make jewellery based on the birds of our fair country (Britain). Whilst I applaud them on their patriotism and support of our nations wildlife, I have to say that they are not even nearly as exciting as a toucan. A chaffinch stands no chance against the toucan in the style stakes. Just my humble opinion.  

The toucan measures 10cm across and 8am high, is laser cut from perspex and is hung on a gold or gunmetal plated chain.

name: Ship in a Bottle Necklace
description:
Arrrrrr me hearties! Finally after months of toil the Ship in a Bottle Neckalce be around me neck. Shiver me timbers! 

The design is made so the the perspex fits together in one layer like a jigsaw, making it really light. The bottle is 10cm across.

name: Custom Rockabilly Tattoo Necklace
description:
I designed this necklace for my very own wedding, hence the slogan on the banner. Now available to Swank customers with custom wording on the banner. It's totally up to you what wording you have on the banner anything up to 14 letters including spaces. The banner and the swallows are made from laser cut plywood and the lettering and hearts are glitter perspex. You can choose the colour of your glitter perspex. The colour options include red, blue, pink, gold or black all in glitter. The necklace comes on a gold or silver chain. That, also is up to you. After purchasing the necklace from the website either write your lettering and choices on the paypal comments box or email swank.jewelllery@gmail.com Any questions just email.

Please allow 12 working days for delivery.

name: Hot Rod Necklace
description:
Show your affection for classic cars, Bugsy Malone or stylish retro engineering with this Hot Rod necklace. The design is created from a real life car owned by my best mate! Yes, she is one cool lady. The hot rod necklace comes laser cut from silver mirrored perspex or ply wood. The lighter option of ply wood is plain and the darker option has been stained and then lightly sanded. The car is quite big measuring 12cm across.

For custom colours please email me swank.jewellery@gmail.com

name: Lucha Libre Earrings
description:
Hola! Brand spanking new to Swank these Mexican wrestling mask earrings. Show your love of all things Mexican and fighty in these blinging beauties. The wrestling mask earrings are laser cut from Perspex and come in three different colour ways, please see the options. Each earring in a pair is different as shown on the picture. 

Beware! These are quite big earrings measuring a mighty 4cm across and 4.5cm vertically, not for the faint hearted.

name: KAPOW! Necklace
description: Can you Adam and Eve it? I designed these necklaces for a friend's pop art themed wedding. How cool is that? If you fancy channelling Andy Warhol through your neckwear then this pop art necklace might be just the thing. The KAPOW! is 10cm across and comes in bright green or purple glitter. Both are laser cut from Perspex.

name: BANG! Necklace
description:
It says BANG! It's bright red, or bright red glitter. Get that guy to notice you in this eye catching necklace, then talk to him about those old Batman episodes or comics or where you got that amazing necklace. It looks cool and it'll get you the guy. Laser cut from perspex this beauty measures 10cm across.

No guarantee of a date. No money back for lack of snogs.

name: BLAM! Necklace
description: Bag your self a comic book punch up inspired necklace in a girly colour! Or even in glitter, what could be more heroine chic that a pink glitter BLAM! necklace? Laser cut from perspex, this baby comes in pink or pink glitter and measures 10cm across.

name: WHAAM! Necklace
description: Next time someone pisses you off you can get all Lichtenstein on their asses with this pop art inspired necklace. The comic book-esque necklace is laser cut from Perspex, comes in bright yellow or gold glitter and measures 11cm ac

name: Rock Lobster!
description:
Not made of rock, simply named after the catchy tune! 

If you like me are a fan of crustaceans, you may like to sport this amazing lobster necklace. Designed by me and laser cut from perspex this nipppy beauty comes in baby pink, mirrored gold and mirrored red. Please flick through the pics to see them all in thier glory.

 Buyers beware the lobster is a massive 12cm across and 6cm high! The lobster necklace is designed by my and laser cut by a small company in th UK. I assemble all the jewellery myself.

For custom designs and colours please contact me.

name: AAAARGH Necklace
description:
You might have a calm exterior, but just below your skin, you're screaming. Let others know of your inner anger with the AAAARGH necklace. Designed and hand made by me and laser cut from perspex these necklaces are bound to get you noticed. The colour options are mirrored gold, mirrored silver and white. All colours are backed on black perspex. This large statement necklace is 12cm wide and 4cm high and hangs just between your collar bones. 

For custom colours and designs places contact me.

name: Sharks and Fishes
description:
Dur...Dur... Dur...Dur...Dur...Dur...Dur..Dur..Dur.Dur (repeat and increase in tempo)

It's Jaws!! Yeah, yeah, Jaws is the name of the film not the shark, whatever. I like sharks, especially cute looking sharks chasing cartoon yellow fishies like these. Laser cut from perspex and string onto silver plated chain the shark is 6cm wide.

name: F1-15 Fighter Jet Necklace
description:
As seen in the skys of Top Gun! These blingin' beauties are pretty much my fave thing on the site. 

Designed by me and laser cut out of perspex these beauties come in gold or silver mirrored perspex, or black perspex. 

The chains are all recycled from unwanted jewellery. This means the chains on the necklace may not be exactly the same as on the images here, but they will be similar.

The jet measures 8cm across and 4 cm high. The tiny bomb will hang in your cleavage!

For custom colours please contact me.

name: Grenade Earrings
description: BOOM! Who wouldn't want golden grenades on thier ears? Designed and made by me and laser cut from perspex these are 4.5cm high. They come in black, gold or silver perspex

name: Grumman Wildcat Necklace
description:
Old school Wildcat plane with tiny Swank bomb dangling below. Chucks Away!

Designed by me and laser cut out of perspex these beauties come in gold or silver mirrored perspex, or black perspex. 

The chains are all recycled from unwanted jewellery. This means the chains on the necklace may not be exactly the same as on the images here, but they will be similar.

The jet measures 8cm across and 4 cm high. The tiny bomb will hang in your cleavage!

For custom colours please contact me.

name: Bomb Earrings
description:
These go great with the F1-15, Wilcat or Bombs necklaces. They look equally ace on thier own. 

Designed by me and laser cut, measuring approx 5cm long these babies come in gold or silver mirrored perspex of black perspex. 

Please contact me for custom colours.

name: Tank Necklace
description: Boom! It's big, it's gold. Its a big, golden tank! This baby is designed by Becky Wignell, laser cut in the UK and put together by thte hands of Becky as well. Measuring 10cm across this beauty is not for the faint hearted jewellery wearer!

name: It's the bomb!
description:
You'll be the bomb with this necklace! Three perspex bombs descending across your chest. 

The bombs on this necklace come in Gold or silver mirrored perspex and the largest measures 8cm by 3cm. They are designed by my and laser cut by a small company in th UK. I assemble all the jewellery myself.

All chain is recycled, reclaimed from unwanted jewellery. This means the chains on the necklace may not be exactly the same as on the images here, but they will be similar.

For custom colours please contact me.

name: Bat Necklace
description: Totally batty necklace with googly eyes! Designed by me and laser cut from perspex the bat is 8cm across and hangs just between your collar bones. comes in red, purple, black and of course pink...... you get pink bats, don't you?

name: Cutlass Earrings
description: Arrrrr me hearties! Be the envy of all ye pirate crew with this booty. Gold or Silver 12cm of piratey joy. All findings silver, gold or black plated. If ye be needing pure gold or silver please email swank.jewellery@gmail.com

name: Stormy Weather
description:
"It's like thunder, lightning, the way you love me is frightening"

When you're singing in the rain express your love for all things stormy with this perspex necklace. All the tiny charms are on silver plated chain and the necklace measures 8cm across.

name: Triple Fighter Jet Necklace
description:
Not satisfied with one jet on your necklace? Me neither! Why not spend the extra cash and get three?

Designed by my good self these babies come in gold or silver mirrored perspex, or black perspex and the largest measures 8cm across.

All chain is recycled from unwated jewellery. This means the chains on the necklace may not be exactly the same as on the images here, but they will be similar.

For custom colours please contace me.

name: Art Nouveau Cat Necklace
description: This is a classy piece for Swank, I must be growing up! An art nouveau style cat last cut from plywood which I have stained different shades. The cat hangs right between the collar bones and looks very snazzy indeed. The back panel is 16.5 cm across.

name: Alternative Wedding Jewellery
description:
Ever wanted something really specific to you on your wedding day? Are you having the sort of wedding which your great aunt's pearls don't quite fit in with? Swank is now moving into alternative wedding jewellery. Having done some for a friends wedding last year I really loved having my jewellery part of someone's special day and as I am getting hitched this year I have started to realise how hard it is to get individual things for a reasonable price. Weddings are expensive, but I won't charge you any more than I usually would just because it's a wedding.

If it's custom made, plastic laser cut wedding jewellery you are after, look no further.

Please contact me on swank.jewellery@gmail.com with your ideas for chat and a quote. Please ignore the price on here, it's just I can't list anything without a price.

name: Rapper Lego Man Necklace
description:
When you hangin in the hood, 
Cruising for a man, 
You need to attract attention, 
However you can, 

With his gold microphone,
And his ghetto blaster,
This lego rapper necklace,
Will get you noticed faster,

Hangin out round your neck on an 18' chain,
None of the fellas are gonna compain,
When they see this lego rapper,
There on your chest,
They're gonna holla at the lady who's the best. (thats you)

name: Artist Lego Man Necklace
description:
Having a creative block? Unleash your inner artist with this lego man round your neck. 

This necklace will be custom made and take 1-3 weeks to arrive with you. 

20" silver plated chain

description:
Gnome is where the heart is! There's no place like Gnome. Sweet gnome Alabama??

This necklace will be custom made and will take 1-2 weeks to arrive with you.

20" silver plated chain

description:
Does exaxtly what it says on the tin! 

This necklace will be custom made and will take 1-2 weeks to arrive with you.

20" silver plated chain

name: Frankenstein Lego Man Necklace
description:
Ok, I know, I know, the guy was called Frankenstein, this is Frankenstein's monster. 

I make these up as the are ordered so it could take between 1-3 weeks to arrive at your door.

20" silver plated chain

name: Hazmat Lego Man Necklace
description:
You have every right to look worries hazmat lego man!

The gun is not glued to his hand so you can remove it if you choose, it is a bit much on the necklace but I wanted to give people the option. 

This necklace will be custom made and will take 1-2 weeks to arrive with you.

20" silver plated chain

name: Werewolf Lego Man Necklace
description:
A-Wooooooooooo! If your fur stands on end of a full moon and you wake up naked next to a half eaten sheep or you just love teen wolf, you can now wear the werewolf lego man with pride. Comes complete with bone and attractive beads!

This necklace will be custom made and will take 1-2 weeks to arrive with you.

name: Geisha Lego Necklace
description:
Complete your outfit with a taste of the orient with this geisha lego man necklace. She’ll bring you tea, fan you, entertain you and look bloody good doing it. 

This necklace will be custom made and will take 1-2 weeks to arrive with you.

20" silver plated chain

name: Punk Lego Man Necklace
description:
Who would’ve thought that dreams come true, and who would’ve thought I’d end up with a lego man like you. My absolute favourite of all the lego men I have made into jewellery so far! I was so over excited when I saw the punk lego man, complete with Mohawk, safety pins in his jeans, sugar skull tee shirt AND a flying v guitar, he’s pretty much 15 year old self’s perfect man! If you too spent your teens getting your face smashed against studded jackets in the mosh pit cos you only came up to shoulder height on most of the men, then this is the necklace for you! He could’ve been on the cover of punk and disorderly. Oi Oi Oi. 

20" silver plated chain.

This necklace will be custom made and will take 1-2 weeks to arrive with you.

name: Surf Chick Lego Necklace
description:
The only sport I have ever had a serious interest in is surfing and am in awe of any girl I see who is even halfway good. I am semi-rubbish, but I try, and as my friend says, the best surfer is the one having the most fun! If you are a surf chick support the women surfers and wear your lego surfer girl with pride. She comes wearing a wetsuit and carrying a board. 

This necklace will be custom made and will take 1-2 weeks to arrive with you.

20" silver plated chain.

name: Extra Special legoman necklaces
description:
Here you can get all the special lego men I have in stock. If you have a particular Lego man you would like on a necklace then see the custom made Lego man necklace listing. Scroll through the images to see all the little dudes. Select the one you want in the options! 

I custom make these necklaces so please allow 2-3 weeks for delivery.

name: Custom Made Laser Cut Necklace
description: Get any thing you want laser cut into a necklace. What? Anything? Yes, that's right, anything. Send me a pic or just tell me what you want and I'll create it especially for you. I can laser cut out of any colour perspex, wood of different types possibly on request and maybe for a tad more money. The pics are of necklaces I have made for mates.

name: mmmm lego
description: Super Lego brick stud earrings which come in various crazy colours. Just check the options to see what colours are available.

name: Batman Legoman Necklace
description: My all time favorite of the super heroes Batman. I make these to order, the price of buying the figure is quite high a fluctuates quite a lot so if you would like one please email me at swank.jewellery@gmail.com and I will quote you a price. It will take up to two weeks for the bat to fly out of the sky down to your post box.

name: Custom made lego man neckalce
description:
Now you can have any Lego figure you fancy on a necklace! Ignore the price I have written, if you email swank.jewellery@gmail.com me telling me what Lego man you would like then I can tell you the price. That is only because the prices of Lego figures vary so much. Please allow two weeks or more for delivery as I have to source componants for lego men and get them posted to me. 

Suggestions I have for figures are
Star Wars; Darth Vader, Obe Wan, Chewbacca, any star wars character.
Harry Potter; I haven’t watched the films or read the books but I can do pretty much any character.
Batman; Robin, Cat woman, Joker, Two Face the list goes on.
Spiderman.
Flintstones; yes they come in Lego!
Spacemen; you get them in most colours
Knights.
Pirates; Arrrr
Robin Hood
Police.

You get the picture; pretty much anything can be done! I could even try to make a Lego figure which looked like you! You could send me a picture! I have made necklaces with boy and girl friends on which looked like the people. 

Chain is silver plated and comes in thick chain (for boys or hardcore girls) and thin chain for laaaadiies! You will also get some random sparkley beads and dice on the necklaces to be decorative!
